<file path="SECURITY.md">
# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Version | Supported |
|---------|-----------|
| 1.0.x   | Yes       |

## Privacy Design

tekflow is designed from the ground up to be 100% offline and private:

- **No network calls** — the app never connects to any server
- **No analytics or tracking** — zero telemetry
- **SMS data stays local** — bank SMS are read and stored only on your device
- **Biometric data never accessed** — App Lock delegates entirely to Android BiometricPrompt; tekflow never reads or stores your fingerprint or face data
- **No cloud sync** — backups are exported as local files only

## Reporting a Vulnerability

If you discover a security vulnerability, please **do not open a public issue**.

Instead, email: **security@[your-domain].com** (replace with your actual email)

Include:
- Description of the vulnerability
- Steps to reproduce
- Potential impact
- Suggested fix (if any)

You will receive a response within 48 hours. If the issue is confirmed, a patch will be released as soon as possible.
</file>

